{"vv17:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv17:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv17:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv17:0.4":"17. Kesakarivimanavatthu ","vv17:1.1":"“Idam vimanam ruciram pabhassaram, ","vv17:1.2":"Veluriyathambham satatam sunimmitam; ","vv17:1.3":"Suvannarukkhehi samantamotthatam, ","vv17:1.4":"Thanam mamam kammavipakasambhavam. ","vv17:2.1":"Tatrupapanna purimacchara ima, ","vv17:2.2":"Satam sahassani sakena kammuna; ","vv17:2.3":"Tuvamsi ajjhupagata yasassini, ","vv17:2.4":"Obhasayam titthasi pubbadevata. ","vv17:3.1":"Sasi adhiggayha yatha virocati, ","vv17:3.2":"Nakkhattarajariva tarakaganam; ","vv17:3.3":"Tatheva tvam accharasanganam imam, ","vv17:3.4":"Daddallamana yasasa virocasi. ","vv17:4.1":"Kuto nu agamma anomadassane, ","vv17:4.2":"Upapanna tvam bhavanam mamam idam; ","vv17:4.3":"Brahmamva deva tidasa sahindaka, ","vv17:4.4":"Sabbe na tappamase dassanena tan”ti. ","vv17:5.1":"“Yametam sakka anupucchase mamam, ","vv17:5.2":"‘Kuto cuta tvam idha agata’ti; ","vv17:5.3":"Baranasi nama puratthi kasinam, ","vv17:5.4":"Tattha ahosim pure kesakarika. ","vv17:6.1":"Buddhe ca dhamme ca pasannamanasa, ","vv17:6.2":"Sanghe ca ekantagata asamsaya; ","vv17:6.3":"Akhandasikkhapada agatapphala, ","vv17:6.4":"Sambodhidhamme niyata anamaya”ti. ","vv17:7.1":"“Tantyabhinandamase svagatanca te, ","vv17:7.2":"Dhammena ca tvam yasasa virocasi; ","vv17:7.3":"Buddhe ca dhamme ca pasannamanase, ","vv17:7.4":"Sanghe ca ekantagate asamsaye; ","vv17:7.5":"Akhandasikkhapade agatapphale, ","vv17:7.6":"Sambodhidhamme niyate anamaye”ti. ","vv17:8.1":"Kesakarivimanam sattarasamam. ","vv17:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","vv17:10.1":"Panca pitha tayo nava, ","vv17:10.2":"dipatiladakkhina dve; ","vv17:10.3":"Pati dve sunisa uttara, ","vv17:10.4":"sirima kesakarika; ","vv17:10.5":"Vaggo tena pavuccatiti. ","vv17:11.1":"Itthivimane pathamo vaggo. "}